## Linear MCP Quick Reference

See **Linear Implement Gate** rule for approval policy (New == Needs Approval, Implement == status_check(Approved)).

```text
Server: plugin-linear-linear
Team: FrenchForest

list_projects                    → stream status overview
list_issues state:"Approved"     → implementable work only (approved issues)
get_issue id:"FRE-8"             → issue details + spec path (check Approved before implementing)
update_issue id:"FRE-8" state:"Done"  → mark complete
save_issue ... state:"Needs Approval"   → new work (always create with Needs Approval)
```
